- Make sure to git init and load all submodules after doing a git checkout on this repository.
- Make sure to do a symlink from .vimrc to this dotvimrc file so that all files remain within the git repo

Commands to replicate:

git clone <this repository> into .vim directory
cd .vim
git submodule sync
git submodule init
git submodule update
git submodule foreach git pull origin master
git submodule foreach git submodule init
git submodule foreach git submodule update
